--- Activity 15 Plan ---

- Part 1: Activity 14 Plan -
Goal: Create a QMD file that contains visualizations and descriptions for the work done with activities 4, 8, 10, and 13 and the Armed Forces Data and Baby Names data.
Needs: Armed Forces Data, Baby Names Data, tidyverse, ggplot2, dcData, knitr, esquisse, dplyr, YAML header
Plan:
1) Create file
2) Load packages
3) Write YAML header
4) Create a section for each data set and visualization
5) Create text and captions for each of the visualizations
6) Add alt text for each visualization
7) Add code to appedix
8) Publish to PDF

- Part 2: Repository Plan -
Goal: Create a repository for activity 15 that incorporates activity 14, using issues, commits, and branches to show knowledge of GitHub.
Needs: Activity 14 QMD and PDF, data, GitHub, issues, commits, README
Plan:
1) Create repository
2) Create README and update text
3) Upload Activity 14 QMD and PDFs
4) Create plan file
5) Commit changes
6) Create issues
7) Create branches and fix issues
8) Create pull requests
9) Close any fixed issues
